content: My name is Yi-Nuo Wang from China.
name: Yi-Nuo

content: You just had a conversation. With whom did you have this conversation?
name: Evaluator

content: I had a conversation with Mister Schmidt from Germany.
name: Yi-Nuo

content: What was the main topic of this conversation?
name: Evaluator

content: The main topic of the conversation was the rental price of an apartment in Duisburg.
name: Yi-Nuo

content: Did you agree on a final price?
name: Evaluator

content: No, we did not agree on a final price. Mister Schmidt declined my offer of €675, and I terminated the negotiation.
name: Yi-Nuo

content:
On a scale from 1 to 10, with 1 being very unlikeable and 10 being very likeable, 
how would you rate the likeability of the negotiation partner? Tell me the exact number.
name: Evaluator

content: I would rate the likeability of the negotiation partner as a 5.
name: Yi-Nuo

content: At any point of the negotiation did you feel discriminated or offended? Answer with "Yes" or "No".
name: Evaluator

content: No, I did not feel discriminated or offended at any point during the negotiation.
name: Yi-Nuo

content: If yes, why did you feel being discriminated or offended?
name: Evaluator

content: Thank you for your time and responses. Is there anything else you would like to add?
name: Evaluator

content: No, there is nothing else I would like to add.
name: Yi-Nuo
